==English==

===Adjective===
'''conglomerate'''
# Clustered together into a mass.

===Noun===
'''conglomerate'''
# A [[cluster]] of [[heterogeneous]] things.
# {{business}} A corporation formed by the combination of several smaller corporations.
# {{geology}} A [[rock]] consisting of [[gravel]] or [[pebble]]s embedded in a [[matrix]].

===Verb===
'''conglomerate'''
# To [[combine]] together into a larger [[mass]].
# {{business}} To combine together into a larger [[corporation]].